b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":197,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"A gift of gratitude from the game\'s director! [Update]","message":"<div>We have sent a present to all players to express our gratitude for your support of Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The present contains one 5\\u2605 Summon Voucher and a total of 100 scales from the various elemental wyrms! We hope these prove useful in your future adventures!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0 The gift:<\/div><div>\\u30fb 5\\u2605 Summon Voucher x 1<\/div><div>\\u30fb Windwyrm&#39;s Scale x 20<\/div><div>\\u30fb Flamewyrm&#39;s Scale x 20<\/div><div>\\u30fb Waterwyrm&#39;s Scale x 20<\/div><div>\\u30fb Lightwyrm&#39;s Scale x 20<\/div><div>\\u30fb Shadowwyrm&#39;s Scale x 20<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0 About 5\\u2605 Summon Vouchers:<\/div><div>\\u30fb The 5\\u2605 adventurers summonable using the 5\\u2605 Summon Voucher are those displayed under 5\\u2605 Adventurer Summon Rates for the 5\\u2605 Summon Voucher in the Welcome Pack at the time of use.<\/div><div>Note: &nbsp;Lily, Naveed, Louise, and Lucretia will be added to the roster of summonable adventurers after the maintenance scheduled for <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1545715800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div>\\u30fb Limited-time 5\\u2605 adventurers are not included in the list of adventurers that can be summoned using 5\\u2605 Summon Vouchers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0 Who gets it:<\/div><div>Anyone who plays Dragalia Lost before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1548741599\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Update <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1546848000\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>Due to positive reception, we are extending these gifts to anyone who plays Dragalia Lost before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1548741599\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1546939800\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>We have confirmed that the above gifts were not correctly sent to players who started Dragalia Lost after <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1546873200\\"><\/span>.<br>This issue has now been corrected.<br>Affected players can receive the gifts by restarting the game.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0 How to claim it:<\/div><div>You can claim the gift from your goodie box via the Home screen.<\/div><div>If it doesn&#39;t appear in your goodie box, return to the title screen and try again.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing the Dragalia Lost game!<\/div>","start_time":1544933100,"prev_article_id":"149","next_article_id":"151","image_path":"","update_time":1546949831}}}'